Title: Relates to certain data required in an annual report on the administration of managed long term care plans
Summary: Requires certain data to be included in reports on the administration of managed long term care plans; changes reporting period to annually.

ActClause: AN ACT to amend the public health law, in relation to data reporting required on the administration of managed long term care plans
